 Because my character can't stick his arms straight up to pull a ladder down.In short:- You don't get much information- The game is hard because you don't get much information, not because of there actually being things you have to overcome.However, if you don't find the above listed issues a problem, then this could be a game for you. Because of the game does deliver on the things it promises."
